title: 9/29/2015: School Times: ‘Snakeskin' photos show Pluto in dazzling details
content: ASTRONOMERS ANALYSING new high-resolution images of Pluto from Nasa's New Horizons spacecraft have spotted ‘snakeskin’ textured mountains on the dwarf planet that are both ‘dazzling and mystifying’. A colour image of Pluto taken by New Horizons...
